{
  "texts": [
    "3, 131301:9 Typical ISAC systemsAccording to the underlying system and software protocol, ISAC systems can be categorized into the radar-centric, communication-centric, and joint-design ones.",
    "Radar-centric ISACFor radar-centric ISAC systems, communication is integrated into the existing radar systems as a secondary functionality.",
    "Typically, communication symbols are embedded in the radar waveform using various modulation techniques.",
    "Due to the high transmit power and high quality hardware of the radar, radar-centric systems are expected to achieve long range transmission.",
    "In order to reduce the overlap with related literature, we review the recent radar-centric ISAC systems based on frequency-modulated continuous wave (FMCW) radar and frequency hopping (FH) MIMO radar."
  ]
}